{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/mapboxmaps\/tilestoreusagemode\/readandupdate"]},{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/mapboxmaps\/tilestoreusagemode\/readandupdate"]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Case","role":"symbol","externalID":"c:@E@MBMTileStoreUsageMode@MBMTileStoreUsageModeReadAndUpdate","symbolKind":"case","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"readAndUpdate","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MBMTileStoreUsageModeReadAndUpdate","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapboxMaps"}],"title":"TileStoreUsageMode.readAndUpdate"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/Overview","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/TileStore-APIs","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/TileStoreUsageMode"]]},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"readAndUpdate"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"All tile requests are converted to tile pack requests, i.e.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the tile pack that includes the request tile will be loaded, and the tile extracted"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"from it. In this mode, no individual tile requests will be made.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This mode can be useful if the map trajectory is predefined and the user cannot pan"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"freely (e.g. navigation use cases), so that there is a good chance tile packs are already loaded"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in the vicinity of the user."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If users can pan freely, this mode is not recommended. Otherwise, panning"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"will download tile packs instead of using individual tiles. Note that this means that we could first","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"download an individual tile, and then a tile pack that also includes this tile. The individual tile in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the disk cache won’t be used as long as the up-to-date tile pack exists in the cache."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/TileStoreUsageMode\/readAndUpdate"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tile store enabled for accessing local tile packs and for loading new tile packs from server."}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"references":{"doc://com.mapbox.MapboxMaps/documentation/MapboxMaps/TileStoreUsageMode":{"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"TileStoreUsageMode","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/TileStoreUsageMode","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"TileStoreUsageMode"}],"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Describes tile store usage modes."}],"url":"\/documentation\/mapboxmaps\/tilestoreusagemode","type":"topic","title":"TileStoreUsageMode"},"doc://com.mapbox.MapboxMaps/documentation/MapboxMaps/TileStoreUsageMode/readAndUpdate":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/mapboxmaps\/tilestoreusagemode\/readandupdate","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MBMTileStoreUsageModeReadAndUpdate"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/TileStoreUsageMode\/readAndUpdate","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"case",